channel.title: How to make aubury teleport you?
channel.description:
Basically, I need to know how to make Aubury teleport you to the essence mines, by clicking the teleport option on the NPC. Spoonfeed would be nice please ;)
Oh and also how to make it so essence gives you more exp. It currently gives 5 per ess.
